{"word":"G4980 - σχολάζω - scholázō - skhol-ad'-zo - Empty","slug":"G4980","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">σχολάζω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>scholázō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>skhol-ad'-zo"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Empty"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03C3;&#x03C7;&#x03BF;&#x03BB;&#x03B1;&#x0301;&#x03B6;&#x03C9; - scholazo&#x0304;</b> - <i>skhol-ad'-zo</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G4981\">G4981</a>; to <i>take a holiday</i>, that is, <i>be at leisure</i> for (by implication <i>devote oneself</i> wholly to); figuratively to <i>be vacant</i> (of a house): - empty, give self."}]}